> Hi, the compat_status structure is struct compat_snd_rawmidi_status64 {
> s32 stream;
> u8 rsvd[4]; /* alignment */
> s64 tstamp_sec;
> s64 tstamp_nsec;
> u32 avail;
> u32 xruns;
> unsigned char reserved[16];
> } __attribute__((packed));
> The rsvd[4] and reserved[16] are not  initialized.

Other members are initialized with zero.
